	<article class="blurb">
		<h1>
			<a href="/read/using-padrino-with-ember-cli-part-1">Using Padrino with Ember CLI Part 1</a>
		</h1>
    <div class="tags">
        <a href="/read/categories/ruby">Ruby</a>
        <a href="/read/categories/padrino">Padrino</a>
        <a href="/read/categories/ember">Ember</a>
